#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>&tellico;</title>"
msgstr "<title>&tellico;</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&tellico; is a program for managing collections. It began as a simple book "
"collection manager, and has expanded to include default collection templates "
"for bibliographies, comic books, videos, music, coins, stamps, trading "
"cards, video games, wines, board games, and file listings. In addition, "
"custom collections can be built for any other type of collectibles."
msgstr ""
"&tellico; je program za upravljanje zbirk. Začel se je kot preprost "
"upravljalnik knjižne zbirke in se je razširil na privzete predloge zbirk za "
"bibliografije, stripe, videoposnetke, glasbo, kovance, znamke, menjalne "
"kartice, video igre, vina, družabne igre in sezname datotek. Poleg tega je "
"mogoče ustvariti zbirke po meri za katero koli drugo vrsto zbirateljskih "
"predmetov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid "What &tellico; Is"
msgstr "Kaj je &tellico;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&tellico; keeps track of the items in a collection, and offers an easy way "
"to enter data for each entry. It provides several field types, and allows "
"for an unlimited number of user-defined fields. The entries in a collection "
"may be grouped by any field for easy organization, and customizable views "
"show as much or as little information as you like."
msgstr ""
"&tellico; spremlja elemente v zbirki in ponuja preprost način vnosa podatkov "
"za vsak vnos. Ponuja več vrst polj in omogoča neomejeno število uporabniško "
"določenih polj. Vnose v zbirki je mogoče združiti po poljubnem polju za "
"enostavno organizacijo, prilagodljivi pogledi pa prikazujejo veliko ali malo "
"informacij, kakor želite."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Loans of items in your collection may be tracked, including a due date. "
"Collections may be imported or exported using a variety of formats, to allow "
"for easy exchange or publication of data."
msgstr ""
"Posoji predmetov v vaši zbirki se lahko sledi, vključno z datumom "
"zapadlosti. Zbirke je mogoče uvoziti ali izvoziti v različnih formatih, kar "
"omogoča enostavno izmenjavo ali objavo podatkov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid "What &tellico; Is Not"
msgstr "Kaj &tellico; Ni"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&tellico; is not an audio or video player. It does not provide facilities "
"for reading or modifying multimedia files. It also does not provide any "
"image-editing functionality. Although &tellico; has some functionality for "
"managing bibliography lists, it is not a full-blown bibliographic reference "
"manager. &tellico; also does not pretend to have all the capabilities of a "
"full-fledged relational database."
msgstr ""
"&tellico; ni avdio ali video predvajalnik. Ne nudi možnosti za branje ali "
"spreminjanje večpredstavnostnih datotek. Prav tako ne ponuja nobene funkcije "
"za urejanje slik. Čeprav &tellico; ima nekaj funkcij za upravljanje "
"bibliografskih seznamov, ni popoln upravitelj bibliografskih referenc. "
"&tellico; tudi ne trdi, da ima vse zmožnosti polne relacijske baze podatkov."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As somewhat of a disclaimer, &tellico; is a hobby for the author, and no "
"guarantees are made about its functionality, usefulness, or otherwise. More "
"information is included in the <link linkend=\"credits\">license "
"declaration</link>."
msgstr ""
"Kot nekakšna izjava o omejitvi odgovornosti, &tellico; je za avtorja hobi in "
"ni danih nobenih jamstev glede njegove funkcionalnosti, uporabnosti ali "
"sicer. Več informacij je vključenih v <link linkend=\"credits\">izjavo o "
"licenci</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid "Terminology"
msgstr "Terminologija"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid "Collections"
msgstr "Zbirke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In &tellico;, a collection is the document. Only one collection exists in "
"each &tellico; file. A collection contains any number of <link linkend="
"\"fields\">fields</link> and <link linkend=\"entries\">entries</link>. "
"&tellico; supports 12 specific collection types by default: books, "
"bibliographic entries, comic books, videos, music, trading cards, coins, "
"stamps, video games, wines, board games, and file listings. In addition, an "
"empty generic collection template is available for any other type of "
"collectibles or lists."
msgstr ""
"V &tellico; je zbirka dokument. V vsaki &tellico; datoteki obstaja samo ena "
"zbirka. Zbirka vsebuje poljubno število <link linkend=\"fields\">polj</link> "
"in <link linkend=\"entries\">vnosov</link>. &tellico; privzeto podpira 12 "
"posebnih vrst zbirk: knjige, bibliografske vnose, stripe, videoposnetke, "
"glasbo, menjalne kartice, kovance, znamke, video igre, vina, družabne igre "
"in sezname datotek. Poleg tega je prazna generična predloga zbirke na voljo "
"za vse druge vrste zbirateljskih predmetov ali seznamov."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid "Collection Fields"
msgstr "Polja zbirke"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each collection may have an unlimited number of fields. &tellico; supports "
"eleven types of fields, which allow for a range of different data. The "
"fields can be edited with the <link linkend=\"fields-dialog"
"\"><interface>Collection Fields Dialog</interface></link> and are explained "
"further in the <link linkend=\"field-types\">Field Types</link> section."
msgstr ""
"Vsaka zbirka ima lahko neomejeno število polj. &tellico; podpira enajst vrst "
"polj, ki omogočajo vrsto različnih podatkov. Polja je mogoče urejati s <link "
"linkend=\"fields-dialog\"><interface>pogovornim oknom zbirnih polj</"
"interface></link> in so dodatno razložena v <link linkend=\"field-types"
"\">Vrste polj</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:206
#, no-c-format
msgid "Collection Entries"
msgstr "Vnosi v zbirko"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An entry is the basic record in &tellico;. Each entry contains a single "
"value for each field in the collection. A collection may have an unlimited "
"number of entries, in theory, although since the whole collection is always "
"resident in memory, too many entries could slow down the application."
msgstr ""
"Vnos je osnovni zapis v &tellico;. Vsak vnos vsebuje eno vrednost za vsako "
"polje v zbirki. Zbirka ima lahko teoretično neomejeno število vnosov, čeprav "
"je celotna zbirka vedno v pomnilniku, zato bi preveč vnosov lahko upočasnilo "
"aplikacijo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&tellico; has been tested with a collection of 10,000 entries, and the speed "
"was satisfactory. However, if many large images are included in the "
"collection, the loading and processing time does slow down greatly. "
"Performance can be improved by having &tellico; store images separate from "
"the data file itself, either in the application-specific folder or a folder "
"relative to the data file. More information can be found in the <link "
"linkend=\"configuration\">configuration section</link>."
msgstr ""
"&tellico; je bil testiran z zbirko 10.000 vnosov in hitrost je bila "
"zadovoljiva. Če pa je v zbirko vključenih veliko velikih slik, se čas "
"nalaganja in obdelave zelo upočasni. Učinkovitost je mogoče izboljšati, če "
"imate &tellico; shranjujte slike ločeno od same podatkovne datoteke, bodisi "
"v mapi, ki je specifična za aplikacijo, bodisi v mapi, ki je povezana s "
"podatkovno datoteko. Več informacij najdete v <link linkend=\"configuration"
"\">konfiguracijskem razdelku</link>."

